# === Claude Code / planwright local state ===
#
# Policy: denylist, not a blanket ignore. Shared project config is committed
# (.claude/settings.json, .claude/commands/, .claude/agents/, and planwright's
# tracked default config); only personal/per-machine/transient state is ignored.

# Per-user personal overrides (Claude Code convention).
.claude/settings.local.json

# planwright per-repo local config — agent-maintained override (design.md D-33:
# per-repo/personal overrides, thresholds). Not committed.
.claude/*.local.yml
.claude/*.local.json

# Linked git worktrees created by /orchestrate (design.md D-37). Working copies,
# not source.
.claude/worktrees/

# Optional handover brief — transient per-worktree cache (design.md D-2/D-3).
.claude/handover.md

# === Bootstrap staging ===

# Consumed bootstrap seed — already mined into specs/bootstrap/, kept local only.
specs/_pending/notes.md

# reference/ is tracked for now (bootstrap execution tasks cite it as their
# migration source). It is transient and SCHEDULED FOR HISTORY PURGE before any
# public release — it may contain personal/work data. See tasks.md "Deferred".
